Class View

java.lang.Object
javafx.stage.Window
javafx.stage.Stage
view.View
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.event.EventTarget
public class View
extends javafx.stage.Stage
Creation of the window of the application

This class is used to create the Stage that will be shown to the user composed with the Explorer, the ButtonsControls, the CansFigure and the ButtinsOthers

Author:
Groupe G1
